<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.3.7">
<l>kuraika ḻalka ṇīṭṭimaṇ koṇṭa kōla vāmaṉā</l>
<l>kuraika ḻalkai kūppuvārkaḷ kūṭa niṉṟa māyaṉē</l>
<l>viraikoḷ pūvu nīruṅkoṇṭētta māṭṭē ṉēlumuṉ</l>
<l>uraikoḷ cōtit tiruvuruva meṉṉa tāvi mēlatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O beautiful Vāmana who took the earth by elongating [your feet with] tinkling anklets,</l>
<l>o Dark one who stood to be joined to those that fold [their] hands with tinkling anklets(?),</l>
<l>even though I am not able to praise you with fragrant flowers and water,</l>
<l>your luminous form of light that is talked about is on my soul.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
